Luxurious and intoxicating, this Eau de Toilette opens with a top note of cardamom, fresh basil and pimento. A heart note comprising of vetiver, sweet jasmine and myrrh trails into an earthy base note of suede, patchouli and woody accords, which lends honeyed warmth to this gourmand fragrance. Polo Green Modern Reserve is encased in strikingly green bottle shaped like a miniature decanter, with the iconic crest of Ralph Lauren boldly emblazoned on it.
